name: Bangbang

BangBang
=============

A jQuery plugin to handle multiple tagged input.

Check out the demo:<http://mgsolipa.github.com/bangbang/searchtest.html>


Dependencies
------------
* jQuery (tested with 1.8.3)
* twitter bootstrap

License
-------
* Free (use it, fork it, do whatever)
